snippet.title: Anders Enger Jensen
snippet.description: Musician from Norway, rooted in the 80s and early 90s synth pop genre. Here you’ll find music made with retro keyboards, synths, samplers and more. Collaborating with The 8-Bit Guy, Espen Kraft, Techmoan and various other Youtubers.
